WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.980
In tribute to all these innocent, victims without borders of our time

00:00:08.100 --> 00:00:09.700
(soft music )

00:00:12.100 --> 00:00:13.600
(child's voice) - Dad?

00:00:13.600 --> 00:00:15.600
Why do you still want to show me the Earth?

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:21.500
(Dad) - To help us protect Life my little one.

00:00:22.900 --> 00:00:24.900
Look how beautiful she is.

00:00:27.200 --> 00:00:29.200
(child) - Dad, why are they all talking

00:00:29.400 --> 00:00:31.400
pangolin and accuse China?

00:00:33.700 --> 00:00:35.900
(Dad) - This animal my little one,

00:00:36.100 --> 00:00:36.600
is exterminated by men,

00:00:38.200 --> 00:00:38.700
who slaughter it like so many species

00:00:38.900 --> 00:00:43.400
out of stupidity and complete absence of Love for Life.

00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:49.300
We think it was from it that the disease came,

00:00:49.400 --> 00:00:51.700
we may know one day.

00:00:54.700 --> 00:00:56.700
As for China,

00:00:56.700 --> 00:00:58.700
this is where it all started.

00:00:59.200 --> 00:01:02.300
China becomes the 1st power of the human world,

00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:05.700
, the champion of the exploitation of resources

00:01:06.100 --> 00:01:09.000
and the destruction of all forms of life ...

00:01:09.300 --> 00:01:11.900
of selfishness and greed of men.

00:01:13.100 --> 00:01:15.100
Like all these countries,

00:01:15.100 --> 00:01:15.600
who followed the same path.

00:01:15.600 --> 00:01:21.900
(child) - What is a Papa Virus?

00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:27.400
(Dad) - In my opinion, One more simple life,

00:01:27.800 --> 00:01:29.800
invisible to us.

00:01:30.800 --> 00:01:33.000
Even if science doesn't call it

00:01:33.000 --> 00:01:34.100
a Life.

00:01:35.000 --> 00:01:37.400
(child) - But why is it hurting us so much?

00:01:38.700 --> 00:01:40.700
(Dad) - I don't think it's the virus

00:01:40.800 --> 00:01:42.800
that hurts us,

00:01:42.800 --> 00:01:44.700
rather he seems to react with those

00:01:44.800 --> 00:01:47.100
whose diet is inadequate

00:01:47.300 --> 00:01:49.700
and whose immune defenses are already weakened

00:01:49.900 --> 00:01:51.900
by their way of life.

00:01:52.600 --> 00:01:54.700
So their body over-reacts to the virus,

00:01:54.900 --> 00:01:56.900
to suffocate them

00:01:57.500 --> 00:02:00.200
and take their breath of Life.

00:02:00.380 --> 00:02:02.940
You see…. Almost everywhere,

00:02:03.100 --> 00:02:06.000
Men have polluted the earth,

00:02:06.040 --> 00:02:09.000
to feed or steal its treasures.

00:02:09.500 --> 00:02:11.700
They polluted the oceans and rivers,

00:02:12.100 --> 00:02:14.900
burned forests and destroyed life

00:02:15.200 --> 00:02:17.200
who gave birth to them.

00:02:18.000 --> 00:02:20.100
They destroy themselves

00:02:20.300 --> 00:02:22.300
to always want more,

00:02:22.400 --> 00:02:24.200
always better,

00:02:24.300 --> 00:02:26.300
, to pollute the air, the sky

00:02:26.400 --> 00:02:28.400
and the space around them.

00:02:28.700 --> 00:02:30.700
They smother the Earth…

00:02:30.900 --> 00:02:33.200
and now the Earth is suffocating us too.

00:02:34.700 --> 00:02:36.900
(child) - but it's awful Dad!

00:02:39.200 --> 00:02:41.400
(Dad) - it is much less so than humans themselves

00:02:41.500 --> 00:02:43.500
who have been at war for millennia

00:02:43.600 --> 00:02:45.600
in the name of a nation,

00:02:45.600 --> 00:02:47.000
a skin color,

00:02:47.400 --> 00:02:49.600
of a system, of a thought

00:02:49.700 --> 00:02:51.700
or a belief!

00:02:52.000 --> 00:02:54.000
Much less than these pesticides

00:02:54.100 --> 00:02:56.100
these drugs or waste

00:02:56.400 --> 00:02:58.900
that we swallow then throw anywhere…

00:02:59.100 --> 00:03:01.000
while so many of us are dying

00:03:01.500 --> 00:03:03.700
every day of thirst, of hunger,

00:03:03.900 --> 00:03:06.300
diseases that we know how to cure.

00:03:07.000 --> 00:03:09.000
Everyone sees it

00:03:10.000 --> 00:03:12.000
but almost no one is watching.

00:03:12.800 --> 00:03:14.800
As for Corona,

00:03:15.000 --> 00:03:17.500
even invisible, we all see it

00:03:17.700 --> 00:03:20.200
everywhere and at the same time.

00:03:22.700 --> 00:03:25.100
(the child) - And what do you think it will give now then?

00:03:26.500 --> 00:03:29.000
(Dad) - Since men have lost touch with their hearts,

00:03:29.300 --> 00:03:31.800
many will be affected in their bodies,

00:03:32.200 --> 00:03:34.200
some by disease

00:03:35.200 --> 00:03:38.000
others by these emotions that they do not know how to taste in silence

00:03:38.000 --> 00:03:39.900
and listen calmly.

00:03:41.200 --> 00:03:43.900
Men will also be touched in their minds,

00:03:44.300 --> 00:03:46.300
this temple invented of the little "me"

00:03:46.500 --> 00:03:48.500
that houses all their outdated knowledge

00:03:48.600 --> 00:03:50.600
and constraints of the past,

00:03:50.900 --> 00:03:52.900
filled with greed,

00:03:53.400 --> 00:03:55.400
selfishness and greed.

00:03:57.000 --> 00:03:59.700
Maybe so that we stop believing we are civilized

00:03:59.700 --> 00:04:02.180
and finally become real Humans.

00:04:04.280 --> 00:04:06.220
There was Fear from the start,

00:04:06.600 --> 00:04:08.600
everywhere, wherever we come from.

00:04:10.000 --> 00:04:12.500
Then the deprivation of our so-called freedoms

00:04:12.500 --> 00:04:14.500
by forced isolation,

00:04:14.900 --> 00:04:16.900
the collapse of our false values,

00:04:17.600 --> 00:04:19.600
economic, moral,

00:04:19.700 --> 00:04:21.700
social or political…

00:04:22.100 --> 00:04:24.100
of our beliefs!

00:04:25.000 --> 00:04:27.500
We are now all immobilized,

00:04:27.600 --> 00:04:29.600
totally and massively.

00:04:30.700 --> 00:04:33.400
As an invitation for everyone

00:04:33.600 --> 00:04:35.700
towards a journey into our inner world.

00:04:36.700 --> 00:04:39.000
So that we can really discover Who we are.

00:04:39.400 --> 00:04:41.400
That we are the same psychologically

00:04:41.400 --> 00:04:43.100
all around the world

00:04:43.100 --> 00:04:45.100
without the slightest difference.

00:04:45.900 --> 00:04:47.900
We say we are good and fair most of the time

00:04:47.900 --> 00:04:49.400
and yet

00:04:49.400 --> 00:04:51.400
we keep criticizing,

00:04:51.400 --> 00:04:53.400
to claim,

00:04:53.700 --> 00:04:56.100
to sow chaos in the name of order and morality.

00:04:57.100 --> 00:04:59.200
We all have so much anger,

00:04:59.300 --> 00:05:01.500
of selfish fears and desires

00:05:02.900 --> 00:05:05.200
When we finally look at each other

00:05:05.200 --> 00:05:07.200
And that we accept ourselves as we are,

00:05:07.200 --> 00:05:09.100
in all lucidity,

00:05:09.200 --> 00:05:11.200
and without mask.

00:05:12.300 --> 00:05:15.200
(child) - I prefer to listen to the birds singing outside.

00:05:15.900 --> 00:05:17.900
(Dad) - How right you are my son,

00:05:18.000 --> 00:05:20.000
it's Earth, Gaia,

00:05:20.200 --> 00:05:22.400
She can finally breathe.

00:05:23.000 --> 00:05:25.600
And in this northern hemisphere where it all started,

00:05:25.900 --> 00:05:28.500
spring will finally be able to radiate.

00:05:29.300 --> 00:05:32.500
Like it never has, for so long.

00:05:32.700 --> 00:05:34.700
And little by little ...

00:05:34.900 --> 00:05:37.300
for those who have looked enough into them,

00:05:37.600 --> 00:05:40.700
found peace, serenity, the simple joy of Being

00:05:40.900 --> 00:05:43.300
rather than the pleasure of appearing…

00:05:43.800 --> 00:05:46.200
When those look up,

00:05:46.400 --> 00:05:48.800
they will rediscover how beautiful life is,

00:05:49.200 --> 00:05:51.700
so precious… The air so pure.

00:05:53.100 --> 00:05:55.600
They will see crystal clear waters

00:05:56.000 --> 00:05:58.400
and will hear like you the song of the Living.

00:05:59.700 --> 00:06:02.700
They will finally know how to look at their children and their loved ones.

00:06:03.200 --> 00:06:05.600
They will smile about everything and nothing

00:06:06.100 --> 00:06:08.100
even ... to the unknown.

00:06:09.200 --> 00:06:11.900
And when they touch up on Earth,

00:06:12.200 --> 00:06:14.800
many will give more than they take.

00:06:15.600 --> 00:06:18.200
And maybe there will be enough of them

00:06:18.300 --> 00:06:20.300
to invent a new world,

00:06:20.300 --> 00:06:22.400
devoid of the power of the ego…

00:06:22.500 --> 00:06:25.200
from the world of desire ... and fear.

00:06:26.600 --> 00:06:27.100
(child) - It's sad that we have to get there anyway.

00:06:30.200 --> 00:06:32.200
(Dad) - but darling,

00:06:32.500 --> 00:06:34.500
this is not the first time this has happened ...

00:06:34.900 --> 00:06:35.400
We had them, Diseases like rainbows.

00:06:38.100 --> 00:06:40.700
A simple breeze and the sweetness of a flower,

00:06:41.000 --> 00:06:43.400
of a tree to wrap us.

00:06:43.700 --> 00:06:44.200
Even a handful of men to guide us!

00:06:48.400 --> 00:06:51.500
Some understood, but they were too few

00:06:51.800 --> 00:06:54.400
And our world so compartmentalized already ...

00:06:56.200 --> 00:06:59.000
Humans have a huge heart.

00:06:59.300 --> 00:07:02.100
When they want something, they do it!

00:07:03.400 --> 00:07:05.900
We have created great technologies,

00:07:06.200 --> 00:07:09.300
but we used it to dominate rather than to give

00:07:09.600 --> 00:07:12.300
like those men who went to the moon

00:07:12.300 --> 00:07:15.300
and planted a stupid flag on it.

00:07:17.000 --> 00:07:19.700
(child) - do you think this will end soon?

00:07:20.200 --> 00:07:23.300
(Dad) - I don't know. I have neither hope nor expectation…

00:07:24.100 --> 00:07:26.600
Men have always had their destiny

00:07:26.700 --> 00:07:29.100
in their hearts rather than in their hands.

00:07:29.700 --> 00:07:32.600
There may be many more of us

00:07:32.700 --> 00:07:34.800
this time to open us to life

00:07:35.000 --> 00:07:37.400
and become ... our own light.

00:07:38.500 --> 00:07:40.500
We will see....

00:07:40.700 --> 00:07:43.400
but Life will do whatever it takes to preserve the Earth.

00:07:46.500 --> 00:07:49.100
(child) - Thank you Dad for telling me all this.

00:07:50.500 --> 00:07:53.100
(Dad) - So, are you ready to dream now?

00:07:55.420 --> 00:07:57.920
(child) - Yes Dad, I want to dream!

